2009-02-26  Philippe Gerum  <rpm@xenomai.org>
	
	* RELEASE: Xenomai 2.4.7 (Andalusia)

2009-02-26  Philippe Gerum  <rpm@xenomai.org>

	* ksrc/arch/powerpc/patches: Update Adeos support to
	2.6.24.6-powerpc-DENX-2.4-03 (compatible with MPC5121-ADS
	hardware, see ksrc/arch/powerpc/patches/README).

2008-02-24  Stephane Fillod  <stephane.fillod@thomson.net>

	* src/skins/posix/shm.c (__wrap_mmap64): Make real call depend on
	configure detection (HAVE_MMAP64).
	
2009-02-24  Yi Li <liyi.dev@gmail.com>

	* configure.in: Remove -mfdpic switch. Set by default by
	bfin-linux-uclibc-gcc, and may cause error with bfin-uclinux-gcc.

2009-02-24  Philippe Gerum  <rpm@xenomai.org>

	* ksrc/arch/{arm, blackfin, powerpc}/hal.c (rthal_timer_request):
	Port x86 fix of race window.

2009-02-24  Jan Kiszka  <jan.kiszka@siemens.com>

	* ksrc/arch/x86/hal-common.c (rthal_timer_request): Fix race.

2009-02-23  Paul Corner <paul_c@tuxcnc.org>

	* debian/prepare-patch.sh: Fix patch generation rules.

2009-02-23  Philippe Gerum  <rpm@xenomai.org>

	* ksrc/arch/x86/patches: Upgrade to 2.6.27.19-x86-2.2-06,
	2.6.28.7-x86-2.2-06.

2009-02-17  Philippe Gerum  <rpm@xenomai.org>

	* ksrc/arch/x86/patches: Upgrade to 2.6.27.13-x86-2.2-05.

	* ksrc/arch/powerpc/patches: Upgrade to
	2.6.28.5-powerpc-DENX-2.4-04.

2009-02-13  Gilles Chanteperdrix  <gilles.chanteperdrix@xenomai.org>

	* src/skins/posix/shm.c (__wrap_mmap, __wrap_mmap64): Map only
	part of the underlying nucleus heap.

	* ksrc/nucleus/heap.c (xnheap_mmap): Allow partial mapping in
	user-space of a nucleus heap.

	* ksrc/skins/posix/shm.c (ftruncate): Use XNARCH_SHARED_HEAP_FLAGS

	* include/asm-generic/system.h, include/asm-arm/hal.h: Define
	XNARCH_SHARED_HEAP_FLAGS.

2009-02-12  Philippe Gerum  <rpm@xenomai.org>

	* ksrc/nucleus/pod.c (xnpod_start_thread): Run start hook for
	user-space threads as well.

2009-02-07  Philippe Gerum  <rpm@xenomai.org>

	* ksrc/arch/blackfin, include/asm-blackfin: Prepare for 2.6.28.

	* ksrc/arch/blackfin/patches: Upgrade to 2.6.28-1.9-00 (GIT).

