	* ksrc/arch/arm/patches: Upgrade to 2.6.28-arm-1.2-00.
	
2009-01-19  Philippe Gerum  <rpm@xenomai.org>

	* ksrc/nucleus/pipe.c, ksrc/skins/native/pipe.c,
	ksrc/skins/rtai/fifo.c: Refactor callback management, fixing a
	severe latency issue, and a potential memory leak in both
	disconnect/release handlers.

	* ksrc/nucleus/pipe.c (xnpipe_disconnect, xnpipe_release):
	Introduce lingering close sequence to keep the extra state safe
	after xnpipe_disconnect() is invoked, until xnpipe_release() is
	called for the same channel.

