	may trigger invalid memory reference.

	* ksrc/drivers/testing/timerbench.c (rt_tmbench_stop): Introduce
	RTTST_TMBENCH_NONE to make sure that no attempt is made to delete
	a non-existent task after rtdm_task_init() has failed.

