2008-04-25  Philippe Gerum  <rpm@xenomai.org>

	* include/asm-x86/wrappers* (rthal_irq_chip_enable/disable): Route
	enable/disable requests to unmask/mask PIC routines for
	post-2.6.18 kernels.

2008-04-23  Philippe Gerum  <rpm@xenomai.org>

	* ksrc/skins/native/task.c (rt_task_sleep_until): Provide support
	for infinite sleep, passing TM_INFINITE as the wake up date. Only
	rt_task_unblock() can resume tasks blocked that way.

2008-04-23  Philippe Gerum  <rpm@xenomai.org>

	* ksrc/arch/powerpc/patches: Update to 2.6.24-powerpc-2.1-02.

2008-04-14  Philippe Gerum  <rpm@xenomai.org>

