	port to the bf561.

	* ksrc/nucleus/pod.c, ksrc/nucleus/shadow.c: Enforce CPU affinity
	unconditionally.

	* ksrc/arch/powerpc/patches: Upgrade to 2.6.20-1.7-07.
	
