	thread entry.

2004-08-04  Philippe Gerum  <rpm@xenomai.org>

 	* RELEASE: fusion-0.4

2004-08-04  Philippe Gerum  <rpm@xenomai.org>

	* nucleus/timer.c (xntimer_next_shot): Anticipate the next timer
	shot better.

